#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmyapplication; is a color contrast checker that allows users to verify if "
"their color combinations are accessible for people with color vision "
"deficiencies."
msgstr ""
"&kmyapplication; je preverjevalnik barvnega kontrasta, ki uporabnikom "
"omogoča preverjanje, ali so njihove barvne kombinacije dostopne ljudem s "
"pomanjkljivim barvnim vidom."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessibility"
msgstr "Dostopnost"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kontrast"
msgstr "Kontrast"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmyapplication; allows the user to check the contrast ratio between colors "
"and determine if the result is suitable for people with color vision "
"deficiencies. Users may select colors in a variety of ways, for example, by "
"inputting the hex values manually, or by using the color picker tool to "
"select any color value on their screen."
msgstr ""
"&kmyapplication; omogoča uporabniku, da preveri kontrastno razmerje med "
"barvami in ugotovi, ali je rezultat primeren za ljudi s pomanjkljivostmi "
"barvnega vida. Uporabniki lahko izbirajo barve na različne načine, na primer "
"z ročnim vnosom šestnajstiških vrednosti ali z uporabo orodja za izbiro "
"barv, da izberejo katero koli barvno vrednost na svojem zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contrast ratio check by this application is related to the difference in "
"color between two objects that allows them to be distinguished. A contrast "
"value of 21 indicates a perfect contrast (usually black on white) and a "
"value of 0 indicates that the two colors are the same. The colors are "
"checked against Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (<quote>WCAG</quote>)."
msgstr ""
"Preverjanje kontrastnega razmerja s to aplikacijo je povezano z razliko v "
"barvi med dvema predmetoma, ki omogoča njuno razlikovanje. Vrednost "
"kontrasta 21 pomeni popoln kontrast (običajno črna na belem), vrednost 0 pa "
"pomeni, da sta barvi enaki. Barve so preverjene glede na smernice za "
"dostopnost spletne vsebine (<quote>WCAG</quote>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmyapplication;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kmyapplication;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kmyapplication;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kmyapplication;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &kmyapplication;"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona &kmyapplication;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After opening the application, you will be presented with a screen similar "
"to the one above - this is the main screen of &kmyapplication; and contains "
"most of its features. A randomly selected text color, background color and "
"their contrast ratio will be displayed as an example."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete aplikacijo, se vam prikaže zaslon, podoben zgornjemu - to je "
"glavni zaslon aplikacije &kmyapplication; in vsebuje večino njenih funkcij. "
"Kot primer bo prikazana naključno izbrana barva besedila, barva ozadja in "
"njuno kontrastno razmerje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Text and Background Colors"
msgstr "Izbira besedila in barv ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are five main ways in which colors can be selected for comparison. "
"These are outlined below."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja pet glavnih načinov, na katere je mogoče izbrati barve za "
"primerjavo. Ti so opisani spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Input Hex Values"
msgstr "Vnesite šestnajstiške vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you know the hex values of the colors that you would like to check, then "
"you can input them directly. To do so, click on the hex value of the sample "
"color currently on the screen and type in the desired value."
msgstr ""
"Če poznate šestnajstiške vrednosti barv, ki jih želite preveriti, jih lahko "
"vnesete neposredno. To storite tako, da kliknete šestnajstiško vrednost "
"vzorčne barve, ki je trenutno na zaslonu, in vnesete želeno vrednost."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Picker"
msgstr "Izbirnik barv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a color that you currently have on the screen - for example, "
"from a sample image - then you can use the color picker tool to input this "
"color directly into the application. To do so, click the color picker icon "
"to the right of the hex value of the currently selected color, and click the "
"color anywhere on the screen that you would like to sample. The color will "
"then be selected in the application."
msgstr ""
"Če je na zaslonu trenutno prikazana barva - na primer iz vzorčne slike - "
"lahko z orodjem za izbiro barv vnesete to barvo neposredno v aplikacijo. To "
"storite tako, da kliknete ikono izbirnika barv desno od šestnajstiške "
"vrednosti trenutno izbrane barve in kjer koli na zaslonu kliknete barvo, ki "
"jo želite vzorčiti. Barva bo nato izbrana v aplikaciji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hue, Saturation and Lightness"
msgstr "Odtenek, nasičenost in svetlost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to tweak your current selection to see if certain changes "
"have an effect on the contrast, then you can do so by using the hue, "
"saturation and lightness sliders. These are located underneath the hex value "
"of the current selection. The color selection will automatically update as "
"you make changes to these sliders."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti svojo trenutno izbiro, da vidite, ali nekatere "
"spremembe vplivajo na kontrast, lahko to storite z uporabo drsnikov za "
"odtenek, nasičenost in svetlost. Ti se nahajajo pod šestnajstiško vrednostjo "
"trenutne izbire. Izbira barv se samodejno posodobi, ko spremenite te drsnike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert"
msgstr "Obrni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Invert</guimenuitem> button will swap the two currently "
"selected colors, setting the background color as the text color and vice "
"versa."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guimenuitem>Obrni</guimenuitem> bo zamenjal dve trenutno izbrani "
"barvi, pri čemer bo barva ozadja nastavljena kot barva besedila in obratno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Randomize"
msgstr "Naključno določi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Randomize</guimenuitem> button will assign random colors to "
"both the background and the text colors."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guimenuitem>Naključno določi</guimenuitem> bo dodelil naključne barve "
"tako ozadju kot barvam besedila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contrast Result"
msgstr "Rezultat kontrasta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contrast ratio resulting from your selection will be shown on the top of "
"the screen, together with a short note explaining how well this contrast is "
"suited to text of varying sizes. This text will be updated automatically as "
"changes are made to the color values."
msgstr ""
"Kontrastno razmerje, ki izhaja iz vaše izbire, bo prikazano na vrhu zaslona, "
"skupaj s kratko opombo, ki pojasnjuje, kako dobro je ta kontrast primeren za "
"besedilo različnih velikosti. To besedilo se samodejno posodobi, ko se "
"spremenijo barvne vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorites"
msgstr "Priljubljene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmyapplication; allows the user to save favourite color combinations for "
"future reference. To do so, press the <guimenuitem>Mark as favourite</"
"guimenuitem> located at the bottom of the screen. These color combinations "
"can be accessed again through the <guimenuitem>Favorite Colors</guimenuitem> "
"menu item, as more particularly described in the next chapter."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija &kmyapplication; uporabniku omogoča shranjevanje najljubših "
"barvnih kombinacij za prihodnjo uporabo. To storite tako, da pritisnete "
"<guimenuitem>Označi kot priljubljeno</guimenuitem> na dnu zaslona. Do teh "
"barvnih kombinacij lahko znova dostopate prek menijske postavke "
"<guimenuitem>Priljubljene barve</guimenuitem>, kot je natančneje opisano v "
"naslednjem poglavju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Options"
msgstr "Možnosti menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter describes all application features accessible after clicking "
"the <guimenu>Menu</guimenu> icon in the top left corner."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju so opisane vse funkcije aplikacije, ki so dostopne po kliku "
"na ikono <guimenu>Meni</guimenu> v zgornjem levem kotu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contrast Checker"
msgstr "Preverjevalnik kontrasta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default screen of the application, allowing the user to select "
"colors and view their contrast ratio. The functionality is described in the "
"previous chapter."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeti zaslon aplikacije, ki uporabniku omogoča izbiro barv in ogled "
"njihovega kontrastnega razmerja. Funkcionalnost je opisana v prejšnjem "
"poglavju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorite Colors"
msgstr "Najljubše barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screen will contain all color combinations saved as \"favorite\" in the "
"<guimenuitem>Contrast Checker</guimenuitem> screen. Color combinations may "
"be deleted by pressing the <guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem> button."
msgstr ""
"Ta zaslon bo vseboval vse barvne kombinacije, shranjene kot \"priljubljene\" "
"na zaslonu <guimenuitem>Preverjevalnik kontrasta</guimenuitem>. Barvne "
"kombinacije lahko izbrišete s pritiskom na gumb <guimenuitem>Odstrani</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screen contains a brief summary of the theory behind this application, "
"with an explanation of how contrast works and how best to interpret the "
"contrast ratio in line with the WCAG standard."
msgstr ""
"Ta zaslon vsebuje kratek povzetek teorije, ki stoji za to aplikacijo, z "
"razlago, kako deluje kontrast in kako najbolje interpretirati kontrastno "
"razmerje v skladu s standardom WCAG."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "About"
msgstr "O tem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screen contains some general information relating to the application, "
"such as the authors and the libraries used. There is also a button that "
"allows users to submit any bug that they may encounter to the developers."
msgstr ""
"Ta zaslon vsebuje nekaj splošnih informacij v zvezi z aplikacijo, kot so "
"avtorji in uporabljene knjižnice. Obstaja tudi gumb, ki uporabnikom omogoča, "
"da vse napake, na katere bi lahko naleteli, predložijo razvijalcem."

